channel.title: Rscpkerz error
channel.description:
Hey guys you guys are the guys that know everything so here's my question.
My server runs smoothly then at any random time my server freezes. What i see in the run.bat file when this happens is this.
[code] [java] [21:08:52 25-02-09] Unhandled packet: id = 156 length = 48 data = 10 6 97 118 97 46 108 97 110 103 46 65 114 114 97 121 73 110 100 101 120 79 117 116 79 102 66 111 117 110 100 115 69 120 99 101 112 116 105 111 110 58 32 52 57 52 52 48 1 [java] [21:08:52 25-02-09] Unhandled packet: id = 156 length = 19 data = 11 2 45 116 121 112 101 58 53 51 32 112 45 115 105 122 101 58 49 1[/code]
Im using firescape. Something to do with a unhandled packet apparently so if you know how to fix this error please comment. Thanks.
